data.description: Don't miss out on this exceptional HUGE lot! VA Loan Assumption available! $5,000 flooring repair/replacement credit offered. This fixer upper home offers a peaceful suburban lifestyle with a countryside vibe while still being close to essential amenities, schools, and recreational facilities; and has easy access to major highways, making commuting to nearby towns convenient. Property has a generally flat lot of 1.85 acres which offers endless possibilities, immediate backyard is fenced, and back acreage space is open; create a separate Farmette area for animals, create expansive gardens, or a unique nature landscape. Three existing outbuilding/sheds could be rebuilt or torn down. Front yard tree stumps to be removed by city. Home has central full bath w/secondary ¾ bath and four bedrooms and a generous front living room with large front window of natural light allowing easy gatherings with family/friends. The adjacent oversized dining area also has natural light from back door slider. Sold AS IS. No POA.
